Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.62,0:21:57.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.58,0:21:58.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是干酪乳杆菌
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.33,0:22:01.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在被排出体外前
